          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 140,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Bright-eyed and bushy-tailed, these young mages seamlessly combine boundless curiosity, vigorous enthusiasm, and a complete lack of survival instincts.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
